node.title: Fears people are seriously injured following crash between tanker and car
node.description: Emergency services are responding to a crash near Turua, Waikato, and say initial indications are there are serious injuries.
node.content:
["Emergency services are responding to a crash near Turua, Waikato, and say initial indications are there are serious injuries.", "", "
\nPhoto: RNZ / Claire Eastham-Farrelly\n
", "Police said in a statement the crash between a tanker and car on Orchard East Rd near Turua was reported just after 6.30pm.", "Cordons are in place and motorists are asked to avoid the area."]
